Take MCU-PT & Alarm
Use IoT Custom Cable
MCU-PT (D0) -- Alarm (D0)
Click on MCU-PT -- Programming -- New -- Empty-Python (under Template) -- Create -- main.py. Double click on main.py & Write code.

from gpio import *
from time import *

def main():
	while True:
		print("Program Started")
		digitalWrite(0,HIGH)
		sleep(1)
		digitalWrite(0,LOW)
		sleep(1)
if __name__=="__main__":
	main()
  
Click on Run
